            <p>Aatura Hospital is equipped with advanced technology and state-of-the-art facilities to support our Cardiology Department's efforts. From our cardiac catheterization lab and cardiac imaging center to our electrophysiology suite and cardiac rehabilitation gym, we have the resources needed to provide comprehensive cardiovascular care in a modern and comfortable environment.</p>
        </div>
