            <h3>Patient-Centered Care</h3>
            <p>At Aatura Hospital, we prioritize patient-centered care, focusing on the individual needs and concerns of each patient. Our cardiologists take a personalized approach to treatment, involving patients in decision-making and empowering them to actively participate in their heart health journey. We strive to create a supportive and compassionate environment where patients feel heard, valued, and confident in their care.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

